OL,9,FBike Classes
OL,11,FWithin the TT's collection of races,
OL,12,Fthere are a number of different bike
OL,13,Fclasses.
OL,15,FThese are split into: Superbike,
OL,16,FSupersport, Supertwin, Superstock and
OL,17,FSidecars.
OL,19,FSome riders race in multiple different
OL,20,Fclasses depending on what bikes are
OL,21,Favailable to them within their teams.
