OL,3,CAll you need to know about the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT 2024
OL,6,FSidecars are the only class that
OL,7,Frequires two people - one working as
OL,8,Fthe driver, and the other balancing
OL,9,Fthe bike and helping to steer as a
OL,10,Fpassenger.
OL,12,FThe 2023 Isle of Man TT marks 100
OL,13,Fyears of sidecars racing around the
OL,14,FMountain Course.
OL,16,FThe TT course is made up of 37.73
OL,17,Fmiles of public roads and is often
OL,18,Fknown as the 'Mountain Course' due to
OL,19,Fthe last quarter of a lap, which sees
OL,20,Fthe rider travel over the Mountain
OL,21,FRoad from Ramsey to Douglas.
