OL,3,CAll you need to know about the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT 2024
OL,6,FMany of the riders complete the full
OL,7,Fcourse in under 20 minutes, averaging
OL,8,Fspeeds of 130mph.
OL,10,FA total of 37 milestones are
OL,11,Fpositioned around the course, one at
OL,12,Feach mile of the track.
OL,14,FMany of the corners around the track
OL,15,Fhave been named, some after
OL,16,Findividuals linked to the TT.
OL,18,FFor example, the 'Morecambe Missile'
OL,19,FJohn McGuinness has a corner on the
OL,20,Fcourse named after him.
