OL,3,CAll you need to know about the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT 2024
OL,6,FRace Format
OL,8,FRiders compete in a time-trial format,
OL,9,Fsetting off at staggered times in an
OL,10,Fattempt to set the fastest time around
OL,11,Fthe course.
OL,13,FRaces take place on public roads which
OL,14,Fare closed to everyday users at
OL,15,Fvarious times throughout the two-week
OL,16,Fperiod.
OL,18,FThe event consists of one week of
OL,19,Fpractice sessions, where teams can
OL,20,Fbecome familiar with their bike on the
OL,21,Fcourse, followed by race week.
