OL,3,CAll you need to know about the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT 2024
OL,6,F103 Years of Racing
OL,8,FThe Isle of Man TT is an annual event
OL,9,Fthat has been held on the Isle of Man
OL,10,Ffor most years since 1907.
OL,12,FIt was not until 1911 that the course
OL,13,Fwas extended to what is known today as
OL,14,Fthe 'Mountain Course' made up of 37.73
OL,15,Fmiles of public roads.
OL,17,FSince then, the event has often been
OL,18,Fnamed the 'most dangerous racing even
OL,19,Fin the world', due to the number of
OL,20,Ffatalities there has been while racing.
