OL,3,CAll you need to know about the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT 2024
OL,6,FThe only times the races were
OL,7,Fcancelled was from 1915 to 1919 due to
OL,8,Fthe First World War, 1940 to 1945 due
OL,9,Fto the Second World War, 2001 after an
OL,10,Foutbreak of foot-and-mouth disease,
OL,11,Fand in both 2020 and 2021 due to the
OL,12,FCovid-19 pandemic.
OL,14,FWhere can I watch the races?
OL,16,FThose attending the races in-person
OL,17,Fare encouraged to watch the races at
OL,18,Fvarious positions around the course,
OL,19,Fwith the Grandstand being a popular
OL,20,Fcentral point.
