OL,3,CAll you need to know about the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT 2024
OL,6,FITV4 will also be broadcasting an hour-
OL,7,Flong highlights programme on various
OL,8,Fnights through the TT fortnight.
OL,10,FThe races will be streamed live on for
OL,11,Fthose who are unable to travel to the
OL,12,FIsland.
OL,14,FTT in Numbers
OL,16,FThe current lap record is held by
OL,17,FPeter Hickman who set a time of 16
OL,18,Fminutes and 42.7 seconds in 2018 with
OL,19,Fan average speed of 135.452mph.
