OL,3,CAll you need to know about the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT 2024
OL,6,FThe fastest average lap speed set in a
OL,7,Fsidecar is 119.250mph which was set by
OL,8,FBen and Tom Birchall in 2018.
OL,10,FSince the races started in 1907, 269
OL,11,Friders have died while taking on the
OL,12,Fcourse.
OL,14,FThe Marshals
OL,16,FMarshals are an integral part of the
OL,17,FTT races making sure the event runs as
OL,18,Fsafely as possible.
OL,20,FJust under 2,000 people registered to
OL,21,Fbecome a marshal for the TT in 2019.
