OL,3,CAll you need to know about the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT 2024
OL,6,FAround 25% of those are Manx
OL,7,Fresidents, with 60% from the UK and
OL,8,Fthe remainder from all over the world.
OL,10,FApproximately 600 marshals are needed
OL,11,Fper racing session.
OL,13,FThere are 12 Chief Sector Marshals
OL,14,Fpositioned around the different
OL,15,Fsectors of the course and ten Deputy
OL,16,FSector Marshals.
OL,18,FThe Isle of Man TT 2024 takes place
OL,19,Ffrom Monday 27 May to Saturday 8 June.
